Could I ask you a favor?
by NileCat » Thu 09.30.2010 1:02 pm I was wondering if someone could do me a favor and correct my unnatural English for me at times.Since coco-san is absent now, I think I'm kind of responsible for some questions which require native-ish interpretation.But I always find my answers awkward, to be honest.I'll do my best to help out the questioners in this forum, But it would be highly appreciated if some of you could correct my English whenever you find it odd.Thank you! NileCat
